---
title: Easy BBQ Bacon & Sweetcorn Pizza with Cheddar Cheese & Rocket Salad
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up this smokey BBQ bacon and crunchy sweetcorn pizza. Oozing with
Cheddar cheese and smattered with rocket leaves for a peppery kick, you can pile this on your plate in less than 30 minutes!
